### 创建相关目录

```
mkdir /usr/local/rocketmq
unzip rocketmq-all-5.3.3-bin-release.zip -d /usr/local/rocketmq/
mkdir -p /usr/local/rocketmq/store
mkdir -p /usr/local/rocketmq/log
mkdir -p /usr/local/rocketmq/store/commitlog
mkdir -p /usr/local/rocketmq/store/consumequeue
mkdir -p /usr/local/rocketmq/store/index
mkdir -p /usr/local/rocketmq/store/checkpoint
mkdir -p /usr/local/rocketmq/store/abort
[root@node01 ~]# cd /usr/local/rocketmq/rocketmq-all-5.3.3-bin-release

```



### jvm配置修改

#### mqnamesrv的jvm配置修改

修改bin/runserver.sh配置文件

```
cd /usr/local/rocketmq/rocketmq-all-5.3.3-bin-release
vim bin/runserver.sh
#按需修改如下配置。因使用的JDK版本为8.0版本，则修改下图位置的JVM参数
-server -Xms2g -Xmx2g -Xmn1g
```

![image-20251027163706027](D:\lmgsanm\03-个人总结\03-中间件\RocketMQ\image-20251027163706027.png)

#### broker的jvm参数修改

修改bin/runbroker.sh配置文件

```
cd /usr/local/rocketmq/rocketmq-all-5.3.3-bin-release
vim bin/runbroker.sh
#按需修改如下配置。因使用的JDK版本为8.0版本，则修改下图位置的JVM参数
JAVA_OPT="${JAVA_OPT} -server -Xms1g -Xmx1g"
```

![image-20251027170323672](D:\lmgsanm\03-个人总结\03-中间件\RocketMQ\image-20251027170323672.png)

### broker配置修改



修改conf/broker.conf配置文件，添加如下

```
storePathCommitLog=/usr/local/rocketmq/store/commitlog
storePathConsumerQueue=/usr/local/rocketmq/store/consumequeue
namesrvAddr=127.0.0.1:9876
listenPort=10911

```



### 启动nameserver

```
[root@node01 rocketmq-all-5.3.3-bin-release]# bin/mqnamesrv &

```



### 启动broker

```
[root@node01 rocketmq-all-5.3.3-bin-release]# nohup bin/mqbroker -c conf/broker.conf &

```

